Description.SourceString: The Bluefin storage ship is a massive, all-purpose mobile naval yard capable of storing crates of resources, packed vehicles and ammunition for long-distance travel and beach-to-beach equipment ferrying. The Bassett Motor Society is proud to deliver such a cutting-edge, versatile blue water asset to various countries across Raka, Katoma, and the Alliant Union.
